Package: tinyfiledialogs
Title: A wrapper around the tinyfiledialogs C/C++ library for cross-platform system modal dialogs
Type: Package
Version: 3.19.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew", "Bridge", email = "matt@mfb.gg", role = c("adp", "cre", "aut"), comment = "Creator of Rcpp wrapper.")
    )
Description: This is an Rcpp wrapper to Guillaume Vareille's portable & cross-platform tinyfiledialogs C/C++ library which provides standard modal dialogs 
    for file & folder selections, message boxes, text, and color inputs. These are slightly more versatile than those found within the rstudioapi package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
ByteCompile: true
